metadata.name: Boy Grey
metadata.description:
"A boy  that has worked with the sun  
A boy warmed by the sun  
The Stars are witness  
To his  endless effort  
So when you see the moon dance with him 
Know that he first danced with it."

The blackness of heritage,  
Passed on to him by his seasoned lineage.

A boy  of mysterious aura  
He commands the air with his stare  
And carries the world in his care

A boy with a thousand words  
Even the earth will listen  
To the stories he will tell
